    "Specifically, the Lyapunov optimization was leveraged to transform the stochastic optimization to a deterministic one, and then the DRL algorithm was utilized to deal with it.",
    "Wang et al. [76] studied the sub-channel and power allocation for multi-cell ISAC networks, where multiple ISAC-BSs served their corresponding users and cooperatively estimated the positions of targets.",
    "They maximized the sum achievable rate subject to the QoS constraints of users and CRB constraints of targets.",
    "A DRL-based algorithm was developed to deal with the nonconvex optimization problem, demonstrating superior performance over the DL-based benchmark.",
